links.title: Why Elastic Stock Spiked Today
links.description: Shares of skyrocketed today after the company released its second-quarter results yesterday that beat analysts' consensus estimates. The tech stock was up by as much as 19.2% today and had gained 15.3% as of 11:55 a.m. EST. Elastic's revenue increased 43% year over year to $144.9 million, which was far better than the $130.5 million that analysts were estimating for the second quarter.
